  [[div class="panel-heading"]]
    The Official Wiki of the Sxlaris Universe
  [[/div]]
  [[div class="panel-body"]]
    [[div class="alternate unmargined"]]
      [[div class="news-content"]]
Welcome to the [http://sxlaris.wikidot.com/licensing-and-third-party-content Sxlaris™ Universe], a post apocalyptic version of Earth where an experiment gone awry has lead to the complete destruction of Earth's surface. 
With the emergence of a group known as the SCP Foundation, claiming to be the leading expert of the strange creatures now prowling the surface, and the megacorporations intent on building a new world, the choice is yours:

▣ place your trust blindly in the Foundation

▣ take the stability of being a number for the megacorps, or...

▣ JOIN US, The Kult. We are Nullsec. We do not forgive, we do not forget. Expect us.
      [[/div]]
    [[/div]]
  [[/div]]
  [[div class="panel-footer"]]
    This wiki is the hub of the Sxlaris[http://sxlaris.wikidot.com/licensing-and-third-party-content ™] Universe
  [[/div]]
